{"tid":495578,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"睇返少林足球，唔只一部喜劇咁簡單。","createTime":"2017-12-10T19:27:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-21T10:54:45.000Z","uid":16055,"like":17,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"721695ea8054db7283e07e43ee8bee2f483f6f43","tid":495578,"uid":16055,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T19:27:58.000Z","msg":"唔講搞笑部分<br />\n<br />\n主線故事<br />\n達叔貪錢淪落<br />\n主角一心發揚光大<br />\n每個師兄弟簡簡單單幾句睇到苦況<br />\n再去到全國冠軍<br />\n故事充實又流暢<br />\n<br />\n感情部分<br />\n幾師兄弟睇張相回憶<br />\n達叔重新做人唔貪機票<br />\n到阿梅果段感情<br />\n用時唔多對白又正已經好深刻<br />\n<br />\n配樂<br />\n每次高潮音樂隨之而來<br />\n比魔鬼隊打又另一種配樂<br />\n仲要次次都唔同<br />\n運用得幾好<br />\n<br />\n用電影技巧角度睇<br />\n更加係高分作品<br />\n比起依家好多電影好<br />\n<br />\n題外話<br />\n背景係大陸<br />\n同真實大陸拍出黎一樣<br />\n唔會拍到富麗堂皇假惺惺"},{"pid":"5b7c96dce5a447467c20500cd123e41156974006","tid":495578,"uid":116530,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T19:29:46.000Z","msg":"10分滿分你俾幾分？"},{"pid":"6189770dd793737d6148f4d7de7608a950690fd4","tid":495578,"uid":47276,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T19:37:07.000Z","msg":"8.5"},{"pid":"33bf4ef30f502d64cec064892bd7c510ffdd278a","tid":495578,"uid":111088,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-10T20:18:37.000Z","msg":"真心想知imdb有冇評過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7682f9eda09bebfd6224f665dba3ac5f6739958","tid":495578,"uid":49524,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T01:14:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>真心想知imdb有冇評過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n7.3分"},{"pid":"e3c6728b919b3c4cb3d00f00892d744c86b207c3","tid":495578,"uid":53498,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11T01:44:58.000Z","msg":"成日覺得呢套已經係周星馳最後一套好睇嘅電影,功夫都叫還可以,之後果啲簡直難睇"},{"pid":"1598866d30e8eebf28d336a36a7c5928896ed49d","tid":495578,"uid":16055,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-11